      "content": "i mean a quarter unit is still insulin. if my blood sugar is already in a good spot and i know im not eating anything else before bed, wouldn't it be safer to just skip it? i'm really worried about a hypoglycemic episode in the middle of the night if i take it and i don't have any food in my system.",
